defaultThe guidance for 
defaultiQuanta
default states that forces should use the data to compare themselves against the average of most similar forces (MSF). 
default&#xa0;
default4.2
default&#xa0; 
defaultSenior managers up to Chief Officer level 
defaultblatantly ignored this guidance despite representations from within the performance team.  They 
defaultdemand
defaulted to
default be told ‘what number they were in their family of forces’.
default  If they were
default second they wanted to be first.
default&#xa0;
default4.3
default&#xa0; 
default 
defaultThrough adopting this approach managers would again bring pressure to bear on improving the numbers rather than improving the level of performance.  
default&#xa0;
default4.4
default&#xa0; 
defaultA lack of understanding of twelve month
default/three month
default rolling data also lead to insufficient time being giv
defaulten to initiatives to reduce crime to achieve results.  Instant results were expected/demanded from operational colleagues.
